    {
      "id": "prjsolar",
      "elType": "section",
      "settings": {"padding":{"unit":"px","top":"48","right":"0","bottom":"96","left":"0","isLinked":false},"gap":"extended"},
      "elements": [
        {"id":"prjsolimg","elType":"column","settings":{"_column_size":50},"elements":[
          {"id":"prjsolimgw","elType":"widget","widgetType":"image","settings":{"image":{"url":"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1710075707220-103d36c97ec6?auto=format&fit=crop&w=612&h=564","id":""},"image_size":"full","width":{"unit":"%","size":100,"sizes":[]},"border_radius":{"unit":"px","top":"12","right":"12","bottom":"12","left":"12","isLinked":true}},"elements":[]}
        ]},
        {"id":"prjsoltxt","elType":"column","settings":{"_column_size":50,"content_position":"middle"},"elements":[
          {"id":"prjsollbl","elType":"widget","widgetType":"text-editor","settings":{"editor":"<p><span style=\"display:inline-block;font-size:.75rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#0056A0;background:#e8f2fc;padding:4px 14px;border-radius:20px;\">Renewable Energy</span></p>"},"elements":[]},
          {"id":"prjsolhdg","elType":"widget","widgetType":"heading","settings":{"title":"Solar and Wind Power Generation","header_size":"h2","title_color":"#0056A0","typography_font_size":{"unit":"px","size":24,"sizes":[]},"typography_font_weight":"700"},"elements":[]},
          {"id":"prjsoldesc","elType":"widget","widgetType":"text-editor","settings":{"editor":"<p>Amerigroup is at the forefront of integrating renewable energy sources into our clean energy solutions. Our solar and wind power generation projects are designed to harness the abundant natural resources available, converting them into sustainable electricity. This electricity is then used to produce hydrogen and ammonia, creating a continuous cycle of clean energy production. Our services include:</p><ul style=\"margin-top:16px;list-style:none;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px;\"><li style=\"padding:12px 16px;background:#f7f9fc;border-radius:6px;border-left:3px solid #0056A0;font-size:.9rem;color:#555c6b;\"><strong style=\"color:#1a1a2e;\">Solar Power Plants:</strong> Developing and managing large-scale solar power facilities that convert sunlight into electricity.</li><li style=\"padding:12px 16px;background:#f7f9fc;border-radius:6px;border-left:3px solid #0056A0;font-size:.9rem;color:#555c6b;\"><strong style=\"color:#1a1a2e;\">Wind Farms:</strong> Establishing and operating wind farms that capture wind energy and convert it into electrical power.</li><li style=\"padding:12px 16px;background:#f7f9fc;border-radius:6px;border-left:3px solid #0056A0;font-size:.9rem;color:#555c6b;\"><strong style=\"color:#1a1a2e;\">Electrolysis for Hydrogen Production:</strong> Using renewable electricity to split water into hydrogen and oxygen, providing a sustainable source of hydrogen.</li><li style=\"padding:12px 16px;background:#f7f9fc;border-radius:6px;border-left:3px solid #0056A0;font-size:.9rem;color:#555c6b;\"><strong style=\"color:#1a1a2e;\">Ammonia Production:</strong> Utilizing hydrogen produced from renewable sources to create ammonia, a key component for energy storage and agricultural applications.</li></ul>"},"elements":[]}
        ]}
      ]
    },

    {
      "id": "prjgreen",
      "elType": "section",
      "settings": {"background_background":"classic","background_color":"#f7f9fc","padding":{"unit":"px","top":"96","right":"0","bottom":"96","left":"0","isLinked":false},"gap":"extended"},
      "elements": [
        {"id":"prjgrntxt","elType":"column","settings":{"_column_size":50,"content_position":"middle"},"elements":[
          {"id":"prjgrnlbl","elType":"widget","widgetType":"text-editor","settings":{"editor":"<p><span style=\"display:inline-block;font-size:.75rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#0056A0;background:#e8f2fc;padding:4px 14px;border-radius:20px;\">Green Energy</span></p>"},"elements":[]},
          {"id":"prjgrnhdg","elType":"widget","widgetType":"heading","settings":{"title":"Green Energy Solutions","header_size":"h2","title_color":"#0056A0","typography_font_size":{"unit":"px","size":24,"sizes":[]},"typography_font_weight":"700"},"elements":[]},
          {"id":"prjgrndesc","elType":"widget","widgetType":"text-editor","settings":{"editor":"<p style=\"margin-top:14px;\"><strong>Hydrogen Development:</strong> Leading in zero-emission hydrogen generation and production. Our state-of-the-art facilities and research initiatives focus on optimizing hydrogen production processes to meet growing demand.</p><p style=\"margin-top:14px;\"><strong>Hydrogen and Ammonia Production:</strong> Utilizing advanced technology for sustainable energy solutions. We produce high-purity hydrogen and ammonia for industrial, transportation, and energy storage applications.</p><p style=\"margin-top:14px;\"><strong>Power Grid Projects:</strong> Enhancing Mexico's national power grid with innovative engineering, ensuring stable and efficient energy distribution.</p>"},"elements":[]}
        ]},
        {"id":"prjgrnimg","elType":"column","settings":{"_column_size":50},"elements":[
          {"id":"prjgrnimgw","elType":"widget","widgetType":"image","settings":{"image":{"url":"https://assets.zyrosite.com/cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,w=768,h=553,fit=crop/ALpeJ1OkE5HqbP9Z/h2-truck-station-2-ALpoNRMgwRHjQ9bQ.jpg","id":""},"image_size":"full","width":{"unit":"%","size":100,"sizes":[]},"border_radius":{"unit":"px","top":"12","right":"12","bottom":"12","left":"12","isLinked":true}},"elements":[]}
